The paper discusses a new blockchain protocol that improves the performance of the system by allowing multiple parallel updates to the ledger and converging them at the next step. This suggests that the paper could belong to Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY).
